        "time_label": "2:59 PM",
        "started_at": "2026-05-02T21:59:52.000Z",
        "ended_at": "2026-05-02T23:23:32.000Z",
        "title": "Chat tail stability, sidebar previews, and an explicit CEO identity",
        "summary": "A long thread of interface fixes removes the flicker at the end of streamed replies, keeps the agent sidebar quiet, and stops treating any full-access agent as the bootstrap CEO.",
        "items": [
          {
            "text": "The streaming assistant tail is now preserved until persisted history semantically catches up, so end-of-turn replies stop remounting or briefly reverting to stale content in both the chat and standalone agent views.",
            "commit_shas": [
              "0dbf9681172ba6b7c18b996948965eb14fd1d15b",
              "db539c0242b7d3e009c42ca3ad4619d6fab3c5f4"
            ],
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "Switching standalone agents now refocuses the chat composer via the shared desktop autofocus path, and the agent sidebar reads previews from a dedicated cache so rows don't churn as history entries get evicted.",
            "commit_shas": [
              "a33f494041f19908a4d4ab1c52bb3e01e8a5f1cc",
              "983b01e5e82eef003aa19ab93d2973ebf8dcff0e"
            ],
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "The agent environment status card is now portaled out of the chat input's stacking context, so hovering remote status no longer renders behind the thinking indicator.",
            "commit_shas": [
              "45cb631ccf61f2c29817f09794a54877ebd7bf47"
            ],
            "confidence": "high"
          },
          {
            "text": "CEO bootstrap now matches on the persisted bootstrap agent id instead of the full-access permission preset, so privileged non-CEO agents keep their own role and the swarm harness wakes hibernating agents reliably.",
            "commit_shas": [
              "5283d2f148d9c4895738ef8919c78f4d639afe07",
              "9274780f9bb436c780d94937a6f750cc5d74d786"
